description	"Elite Scout Trooper

^2Weaponry:
- Blaster Pistol (2)
- E-11 Blaster Rifle (1)
- 2 Fire Grenades

^8Attributes:
- 1 Reinforcement
- Stamina (2)
- Dexterity (2)

^3Abilities:
- Sprint ^3[CS1]
- Dex Roll ^3[CS2]

Encased in a Camoflauged variation of the typical Scouttrooper armour, they lie in wait or use their camo to scout ahead for threats using the environment to their advantage."